# Kalodata hub UI (mandatory)

## Never

- Blind coordinate clicks without screenshot verify
- Click filters on **product detail** (`/product/detail`) — LIST page only (`/product`)
- Click outside left sidebar (x > 380 on 1920×1080)
- Press **Submit** if `verify_before_submit()` fails
- Continue when Gemini vision returns 503 — **abort**, do not misclick

## Always

1. `ensure_product_list_page()` — direct URL `https://www.kalodata.com/product`
2. Pre-flight vision — confirm `page_type == product_list` **before** filter clicks
3. `build_spec(method, category)` + coach overlay (price ≥$80, commission ≥8%)
4. Apply → verify → Submit only if pass
5. `--cleanup-tabs` when duplicate product detail tabs (Ovios couch etc.)

## Command

```bash
python3 scripts/hub_kalodata_apply_method.py --method middle_core --category Furniture --cleanup-tabs
```

Swap `--category` per niche; swap `--method` per course filter (hardcore, lurkers, hundred_gap, middle_core, two_hundred).
